T1  - Mean-Variance-Instability Portfolio Analysis: A Case of Taiwan's Stock Market
AU  - Lee, Shawin
AU  - Chang, Kuo-Ping
Y1  - 1995/07/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/07/01
