T1  - Global Disaggregation of Information-Intensive Services
AU  - Apte, Uday M.
AU  - Mason, Richard O.
Y1  - 1995/07/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.41.7.1250
